# module_template.mdc
type: ApplyToPattern
pattern: **/modules/*/module-template

# Scaffold pattern for a module named <module>
- modules/<module>/
  - module.ts
  - <module>.controller.ts
  - <module>.service.ts
  - dto/
    - create-<module>.dto.ts
    - update-<module>.dto.ts
  - entities/
    - <module>.entity.ts
  - repository/
    - <module>.repository.ts
  - MODULE_DOC.md
  - __tests__/
    - <module>.service.spec.ts
  - flowcharts/
    - <module>-flow.svg or .drawio

# Rules
- Use Nest CLI for scaffold: nest g module <module> && nest g service <module> && nest g controller <module>
- Add top-of-file header to each generated file.
- Add logger.debug at entry/exit of all public service methods.
- Add integration tests skeleton that uses testcontainers/postgres.